<style>
.cc-pillar__icon {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--cc-yellow);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: 1;
  font-style: normal;
}
</style>

<section class="cc-pillars">
  <div class="cc-pillars__inner">
    <p class="cc-section-eyebrow">Three reasons to get involved</p>
    <h2 class="cc-section-heading">Play. Connect. Grow.</h2>
    <div class="cc-pillars__grid">
      <div class="cc-pillar">
        <div class="cc-pillar__num">01</div>
        <div class="cc-pillar__icon">▶</div>
        <h3 class="cc-pillar__title">Play More</h3>
        <p class="cc-pillar__body">Never miss a match. We surface the right events for your level, location and availability — so you're always on court, not waiting for someone to organise it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-pillar">
        <div class="cc-pillar__num">02</div>
        <div class="cc-pillar__icon">⊕</div>
        <h3 class="cc-pillar__title">Connect Better</h3>
        <p class="cc-pillar__body">Find your people. Whether you need a regular partner, a last-minute sub, or a doubles pair for a tournament — <span style="text-transform:none">cørt</span> Club makes it easy to reach the right player at the right time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-pillar">
        <div class="cc-pillar__num">03</div>
        <div class="cc-pillar__icon">↑</div>
        <h3 class="cc-pillar__title">Grow Your Game</h3>
        <p class="cc-pillar__body">Your <span style="text-transform:none">cørt</span> Rating tracks every match and rises with your performance. Structured competition means you're always playing with purpose — not just hitting for fun.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

